'''Mesens Corporation''' was a manufacturer of [[Starship/Legends|spacecraft]]. Its [[Orbit/Legends|orbital]] [[Shipyard/Legends|shipyards]] were located over the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Ganzik]].<ref name="Unknown">''[[The Unknown Regions]]''</ref> The [[SCT Scout craft|SCT Scout Craft]], launched [[Standard decade/Legends|decades]] before the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]], was a class of vessel produced by this firm.

